fields.bio: My name is Matt.  I used to work as a zookeeper and now I am a software engineer.  Both of these jobs have such overlapping skill sets!  One thing I really love is not killing off good plants.  I rather give them away than throw out perfectly good growable plants!  So I made this community to share my plants with others.  Please take in some of my plants!
My name is Meg.  I am new to plants, but am eager to learn.
I'm Jenna.  I have a bit of experience with flowering plants.  I want more fruiting plants.
My name ios Bryon and I have been taking care of plants since I was 10.  Looking to share some of mine with you all.
I'm a welder named Emily who likes plants.  I need more plants!
I'm Tyler, and new to plants.  I would like to learn more and grow more.
